; font-family: 'helvetica neue', 'hiragino sans gb', 'microsoft yahei', 'wenquanyi micro hei', sans-serif; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-align: center; line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 15px; font-family: 'helvetica neue', 'hiragino sans gb', 'microsoft yahei', 'wenquanyi micro hei', sans-serif; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-align: center; line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 15px; font-family: 'helvetica neue', 'hiragino sans gb', 'microsoft yahei', 'wenquanyi micro hei', sans-serif; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-align: center; line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 'helvetica neue', 'hiragino sans gb', 'microsoft yahei', 'wenquanyi micro hei', sans-serif; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-align: center; line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 15px; font-family: 'helvetica neue', 'hiragino sans gb', 'microsoft yahei', 'wenquanyi micro hei', sans-serif; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-align: center; line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 15px; font-family: 'helvetica neue', 'hiragino sans gb', 'microsoft yahei', 'wenquanyi micro hei', sans-serif; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-align: center; line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 15px; font-family: 'helvetica neue', 'hiragino sans gb', 'microsoft yahei', 'wenquanyi micro hei', sans-serif; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-align: center; line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 'helvetica neue', 'hiragino sans gb', 'microsoft yahei', 'wenquanyi micro hei', sans-serif; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-align: center; line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>话题：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tWriting: imagine a scenario or express your opinion<br />\n\tVerge<br />\n\tVerge means the edge or tip of something. What does the verge refer to? Why is it important? What will happen next?<br />\n\tThis week's topic: They were on the verge... (90-110 words)</p>\n<p>\n\tSuggestions:<br />\n\t1) standing on the verge of <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/cliff\" target=\"_blank\">cliff</a><br />\n\t2) pushing towards the verge of one's ability<br />\n\t3) on the verge of a panic attack<br />\n\t4) on the verge of success<br />\n\t5) Instead of writing a scenario, feel free to comment on the story below.</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>范例1：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tHodge had no idea how that person found his contact information, nor did he know why out of all people, he was chosen. Perhaps there were others given the same offer, also doing what he was asked to do, but he did not know for sure. He felt his club business was on the verge of making it, and it just needed that little push to make it into the big leagues. That was why he took the hand which was offered to him, and he agreed to work for that person.</p>\n<p>\n\t想要得到专业主持人的点评和意见吗？<a href=\"http://st.hujiang.com/topic/168034992101/\" target=\"_blank\">快来节目现场一试身手吧&gt;&gt;</a></p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p799328/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p799328\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p805092/\">丁宁夺金李晓霞夺银，福原爱爆哭粉丝心疼</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p803529/\">美剧经典台词：只有放弃才是真正的失败！</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p805114/\">英国第三大富豪去世 留给25岁儿子90亿镑……</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p799640/\">美国人评选最伟大的英剧TOP10 有你心头爱吗</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p805028/\">奥运泳池变绿了？！各国段子手开始发威了</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p804703/\">沪江15周年庆，30